rd":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 2037)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 225 - 1080, 2262)","children":[{"index":0,"class":"androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":true,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 2037)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 225 - 1080, 2260)","children":[{"index":0,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 979)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 225 - 525, 1151)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"你是不是经常这样？在公开场合里，不敢表达自己的真实想法和感受总是轻易被别人影响，对自己的目标不坚定做事时扭扭捏捏的，总觉得不好意思其实唯唯诺诺并没有错，只是性格如此，也不代表我们无法做好任何事情。但这个世界总是偏向于爱表达会表达敢表达的人，我们暂时无法改变规则，何不去顺应规则，成为自己。因为这些不是缺点也不是弱点，只是一种行事方法，而方法是可以改变的。从开始看纪录片开始，真实的影音，别人的故事，总会给你意想不到的启发和收获。今天整理了29部纪录片，涵盖六个方面，希望你能从其中一部或者几部里找到对你有启发的纪录片。女性自我成长类消费认知类搞钱认知类人文历史类人生百态类认知颠覆类纪录片会让我们更加了解这个世界，趋近于真相，从而了解自己，成为你自己。我是夏夏专注于写作和女性成长领域从事过销售、服务行业，靠写作成为自由职业者分享写作干货｜成长感悟｜手帐规划｜思维认知｜女性成长感恩所有遇见和喜欢 #纪录片# #纪录片推荐#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(66, 855 - 492, 963)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParen