ge":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 131, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(916, 910 - 1047, 960)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"33","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 40, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(974, 912 - 1014, 957)"}]}]},{"index":2,"text":"地图","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 87, 37)","boundsInScreen":"(599, 994 - 686, 1031)"},{"index":3,"text":"民族","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 87, 37)","boundsInScreen":"(724, 994 - 811, 1031)"}]},{"index":2,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 979)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 1184 - 525, 2163)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"职场人“六宗罪” | 1、工作只会越做越多，还会多做多错工作永远是做不完的，一旦你做得又好又快，领导可不会表扬你，只会觉得你工作不饱和，还能给你再加点。尤其，干得越多，犯错越多。领导只会记住你犯过的错，不会知道你创造了多少价值。2、沉浸在琐碎事务中，没有时间思考和发展很多人都发现了，一旦工作过于饱和，整个人特别累，根本没有精力思考，复盘提升自己的能力。一回到家只想躺下看手机，也没法好好提升自己。3、升职加薪，从来不靠拼命加班很多人勤勤恳恳工作，天天加班，甚至业绩方面也可圈可点，但往往升职加薪却与之无缘。或是沉浸于工作，忽略了团队沟通;或是成绩不被看见，很少在领导面前刷存在感，所以不能一味瞎忙。4、光芒太胜容易树敌，让同事孤立你工作做得太好太快，让周围摸鱼的同事情何以堪?他们会认为你只是想表现出风头，从而排斥你、孤立你。不动声色给你使绊子，甚至主动找你茬。5、打工不要责任心过剩，不该操的心别操在钱给到位的基础上，完成本职工作就可以，不要沉迷老板画饼，不要怯于拒绝同事。打工人要有打工人的坚持，树立边界。薪资是买你8小时的工作内容，不是买走你的情绪，买走你的健康。6、不要太听话，适当讨价还价领导的压迫感，只是在测试你的边界和服从性。工作做不完了，让领导排出优先级;工作有困难了，也别傻傻的自己扛，适当“哭一哭”，也是一种职场智慧。 #职场#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(66, 1867 - 492, 1975)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 1975 - 525, 2081)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"文哥创业笔记","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 198, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(127, 2005 - 325, 2050)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 144, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(381, 2003 - 525, 